data.description: Lovely updates await you in this very large split level home. An extra large entryway in a bi-level split is always appreciated! This foyer also has a large closet and the door to the garage is new. The large kitchen has ample cabinetry and dining space, with a large island and a walk in pantry. Updates include: bathrooms with new flooring and vanities, new carpeting in the lower level, new flooring throughout most of the house, gas range and dishwasher 2022, sliding doors 2020, and more. There is a newly finished hobby room in the lower level that walks out to the backyard, perfect for large pieces of woodworking equipment, quilting, or as a playroom, bedroom, whatever you wish. At 28x24, the garage is extra large, plus it has an area that is about 5x10. In the photos it shows that there is baseboard missing, but it will be installed by the time of showings.
